#[navbar]

#[section, $md:
    @../ (Documentation) / Branching

    # Branching

    Use a normal `if` for one decision. Use a full match when one value has several meaningful cases. Both forms stay explicit about scope, fallback behaviour and the values they produce.

    No mystery fallthrough. No wildcard punctuation pretending to mean three different things.
]

